OL,6,F"It's #7 or #6 for a pint; no wonder
OL,7,Fpeople don't go out."
OL,9,FHe adds: "The town generally isn't as
OL,10,Fbusy, people shop on the Internet,
OL,11,Fpeople don't have money in their
OL,12,Fpockets.
OL,14,F"But also if people don't have money
OL,15,Fin their pockets anyway, but the costs
OL,16,Fare going up, then there is only one
OL,17,Fway businesses will go and that's
OL,18,Fdownwards.
