OL,6,F"I hope they will at least allow
OL,7,Fcompetition, certainly leading up to
OL,8,FChristmas when people can go out from
OL,9,F5pm onwards and we can say drinks are
OL,10,Fhalf price."
OL,12,FMarcus Calvani, of the Jersey
OL,13,FHospitality Association also believes
OL,14,Fthe current laws are "holding back"
OL,15,Fthe industry and "limiting the
OL,16,Fcreativity" of new businesses.
OL,18,FHowever, news of a consultation has
OL,19,Fgiven him hope for the future.
