OL,6,FHe told ITV News: "They are being
OL,7,Fextremely open about it. It looks
OL,8,Freally really positive.
OL,10,F"We have sat down with Public Health
OL,11,Fand the Treasury and discussed how can
OL,12,Fwe make it more affordable to go out
OL,13,F(and) how can we make it a better
OL,14,Fplace to live whilst also making it
OL,15,Fbetter to trade as well."
OL,17,FIt's not just hospitality businesses
OL,18,Fcalling for modification to the rules,
OL,19,Fbut also bands, food businesses and
OL,20,Ftaxi drivers.
