OL,6,FAdam True, singer and guitarist in the
OL,7,Fband 88 Bunkface, says: "We are really
OL,8,Fstuck in the past when it comes to
OL,9,Falcohol promotions and the hospitality
OL,10,Ftrade over here is hindered at every
OL,11,Fpossible opportunity.
OL,13,F"We know it is still a priority for
OL,14,Fpeople to enjoy themselves, but there
OL,15,Fis so much more to be done."
